version_description: This is from watching Zakk on a live session and using the chords he was playing. Please enjoy and comment.
Noticed it wasn't here so knocked up a quick version.
This tab is based off the original studio recording from the Book of Shadows II album (https://youtu.be/i8MDT8pglps).
By listening to the song while playing you can figure out the strumming pattern its not that hard i think and hail Zakk Wylde.
